    "description": "KTC Logistics Holdings Services invites applications from qualified candidates for the position of Warehouse Manager at our Bhopal location. This role offers excellent career advancement prospects.\n\nAbout KTC Logistics Holdings Services:\nKTC Logistics Holdings Services is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Optimize delivery routes to reduce cost and improve efficiency\n• Manage a fleet of vehicles and coordinate with drivers\n• Coordinate with warehousing teams for inbound and outbound operations\n• Coordinate with customer service teams to resolve delivery issues\n• Prepare MIS reports on delivery performance and SLA adherence\n• Implement warehouse management systems (WMS) and track KPIs\n• Ensure proper handling, packaging, and labeling of goods\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Chartered Accountant (ICAI)\n• 1-3 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in SAP SCM\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain Management\n• Proficiency in Last Mile Delivery\n• Proficiency in Fleet Management\n• Proficiency in Data Analytics\n• Proficiency in 3PL Management\n• Proficiency in GPS Tracking Systems\n• Proficiency in TMS\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Flexible working hours\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Salary Range: 4 LPA - 9 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Bhopal, Madhya Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with KTC Logistics Holdings Services!",
